        "\n",
        "# What are AI agents?\n",
        "\n",
        "Traditional programs follow a fixed path. Agents decide what to do next.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Traditional code vs. agents\n",
        "\n",
        "| Traditional code | AI agent |\n",
        "|:---|:---|\n",
        "| Fixed logic paths | Dynamic decision-making |\n",
        "| Needs exact instructions | Figures out \"how\" from \"what\" |\n",
        "| Fails on edge cases | Adapts and retries |\n",
        "| No external awareness | Can browse, query, research |\n",
        "| Stateless | Maintains context and memory |\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## The four components of an agent\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Brain (LLM)** — reasoning, language understanding, code generation\n",
        "2. **Tools** — file operations, web access, code execution, APIs\n",
        "3. **Planning** — sequential, conditional, iterative, hierarchical\n",
        "4. **Memory** — short-term (this conversation), long-term (past sessions), working (current task)\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.fragment}\n",
        "The LLM is the brain in a jar. The agent framework is the mech suit — it gives the brain hands, eyes, and memory.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Traditional vs. agentic approach {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        ":::: {.columns}\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
        "**Traditional:**\n",
        "```python\n",
        "def summarize(url):\n",
        "    html = fetch_url(url)\n",
        "    text = extract_text(html)\n",
        "    return run_summarizer(text)\n",
        "```\n",
        "Fixed steps. Breaks if the page is a PDF, behind a login, or in another language.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
        "**Agentic:**\n",
        "```python\n",
        "class ArticleAgent(Agent):\n",
        "    def run(self, topic):\n",
        "        results = self.search_web(topic)\n",
        "        urls = self.filter_relevant(results)\n",
        "        for url in urls:\n",
        "            content = self.fetch(url)\n",
        "            if self.is_complex(content):\n",
        "                self.deep_analysis(content)\n",
        "            else:\n",
        "                self.quick_summary(content)\n",
        "        return self.synthesize_report()\n",
        "```\n",
        "The agent **decides** what steps are needed.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::::\n",
        "\n",
