        "\n",
        "# OpenCode\n",
        "\n",
        "A CLI-first AI coding agent.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Why OpenCode?\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Privacy-first** — code stays on your machine\n",
        "- **Multi-session** — run parallel agents on the same project\n",
        "- **75+ model providers** — free models, paid models, local models\n",
        "- **Terminal-native** — works entirely in the CLI\n",
        "- **Extensible** — custom skills teach the AI domain knowledge\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Installation {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        ":::: {.columns}\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"33%\"}\n",
        "**macOS**\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "brew tap anomaly/opencode\n",
        "brew install opencode\n",
        "```\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"33%\"}\n",
        "**Linux**\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "curl -fsSL \\\n",
        "  https://opencode.ai/install \\\n",
        "  | bash\n",
        "```\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"34%\"}\n",
        "**Windows**\n",
        "```powershell\n",
        "winget install \\\n",
        "  Anomaly.OpenCode\n",
        "```\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::::\n",
        "\n",
        "Then configure:\n",
        "\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "opencode configure\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "Select a model provider, paste your API key, pick a model.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## OpenRouter — one key, 300+ models {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        "Instead of signing up for OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google separately, use **OpenRouter** as a single gateway.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Feature | OpenRouter | Direct API |\n",
        "|---|---|---|\n",
        "| Cost | Free tier + pay-per-use | Requires paid key |\n",
        "| Models | 300+ from all providers | One provider only |\n",
        "| Setup | One API key | Separate accounts each |\n",
        "\n",
        "**Free models for students:**\n",
        "\n",
        "- `openai/gpt-4o-mini` — fast and capable\n",
        "- `google/gemini-flash-1.5` — good for long conversations\n",
        "- `meta-llama/llama-3.1-8b-instruct` — open source\n",
        "\n",
        "Start free. Upgrade when you hit limits.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## OpenCode Zen — premium Chinese models {.smaller}\n",
        "\n",
        "Access to high-performance Chinese models at reduced cost:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **MinMax M2.5** — 80.2% on SWE-Bench, ~$1/hour, strong Claude alternative\n",
        "- **Kimi K2.5** — 1T parameter MoE model, 32B active params, open-weight\n",
        "\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "opencode configure\n",
        "# Select \"OpenCode Zen\" → paste Zen API key → choose model\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Custom skills\n",
        "\n",
        "Teach OpenCode domain-specific knowledge with SKILL.md files:\n",
        "\n",
        "```markdown\n",
        "---\n",
        "name: my-skill\n",
        "description: What this skill does\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "Instructions for the AI when this skill is invoked...\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "Place in `.opencode/skills/my-skill/SKILL.md` for project-level, or `~/.opencode/skills/` for global.\n",
